
HELP:
    [bch-hack help foo] will give help on subcommand foo.
    [bch-hack help foo bar] will give help on subcommand foo bar.

ABOUT:
    This program is a front end to allow the quick development
    and deployment of little software tools. Development takes
    place in the repository rooted at [$BCH_HACK_ROOT]. An app
    is a subdirectory of [$BCH_HACK_ROOT/apps] which contains
    an executable [main] script.
